---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Section from "@/components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Header title="Frequently asked questions" />
  <Section title="What is Mehad?">
    <p>
      Mehad is an Egyptian fashion brand specializing in elegant, modest women's
      clothing. We focus on refined design, precise tailoring, and high-quality
      fabrics, creating timeless pieces that combine comfort, style, and
      longevity.
    </p>
  </Section>
  <Section title="Is Mehad an Egyptian brand?">
    <p>
      Yes. Mehad designs and produces its collections entirely in Egypt. Every
      piece is developed locally with a deep understanding of the lifestyle and
      expectations of women who value quality and thoughtful design.
    </p>
  </Section>
  <Section title="Who does Mehad design for?">
    <p>
      Mehad collections are designed for women who seek elegance and confidence.
      Our core audience includes women who prefer sophisticated, well-crafted
      styles over fast-fashion trends.
    </p>
  </Section>
  <Section title="How can I pay for my order?" separator={false}>
    <p>
      All orders are fulfilled using Cash on Delivery (COD).
      <br />
      Orders are placed through the website and payment is collected in cash by the
      courier upon delivery.
    </p>
  </Section>
</Layout>
